trans-unit.source: Base designer class for extending the design mode behavior of a root design document that supports nested components.
<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ComponentDocumentDesigner> provides a base class for designers of root design documents that support nested components.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ComponentDocumentDesigner> 支持嵌套的组件的根设计文档的设计器提供基类。

trans-unit.source: In addition to the methods and functionality inherited from the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner> class, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ComponentDocumentDesigner> implements the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IRootDesigner> interface to provide a root-level design mode view for the associated component, and any nested components.
trans-unit.target: 除了的方法和功能从继承<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner>类，<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ComponentDocumentDesigner>实现<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IRootDesigner>接口，以提供根级别设计模式视图关联的组件和任何嵌套组件。

trans-unit.source: The root-level design mode view for a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form> or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control> is typically provided by a built-in root designer.
trans-unit.target: 根级别设计模式视图<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form>或<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control>通常由内置根设计器。

trans-unit.source: A custom <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IRootDesigner> implementation is required to provide a view for other types of root components in design mode.
trans-unit.target: 自定义<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IRootDesigner>实现需要为其他类型的根组件在设计模式下提供视图。

trans-unit.source: You can associate a designer with a type using a <xref:System.ComponentModel.DesignerAttribute>.
trans-unit.target: 你可以将一个设计器关联类型使用<xref:System.ComponentModel.DesignerAttribute>。

trans-unit.source: For an overview of customizing design time behavior, see [Extending Design-Time Support](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/d6ac8a6a-42fd-4bc8-bf33-b212811297e2).
trans-unit.target: 有关自定义设计时行为的概述，请参阅[扩展设计时支持](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/d6ac8a6a-42fd-4bc8-bf33-b212811297e2)。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ComponentDocumentDesigner" /> class.
Gets the control for the designer.
The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Control" /> the designer is editing.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Control" />编辑设计器。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <see langword="false" /> to release only unmanaged resources.
Releases the unmanaged resources used by the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ComponentDocumentDesigner" /> and optionally releases the managed resources.
This method is called by the public `Dispose()` method and the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 此方法称为由公共`Dispose()`方法和<xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: `Dispose()` invokes the protected `Dispose(Boolean)` method with the `disposing` parameter set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: `Dispose()` 调用受保护`Dispose(Boolean)`方法替换`disposing`参数设置为`true`。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invokes `Dispose` with `disposing` set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> 调用`Dispose`与`disposing`设置为`false`。

trans-unit.source: When the `disposing` parameter is true, this method releases all resources held by any managed objects that this <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ComponentDocumentDesigner> references.
trans-unit.target: 当`disposing`参数为 true 时，此方法释放由任何托管对象持有的全部资源此<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ComponentDocumentDesigner>引用。

trans-unit.source: This method invokes the `Dispose()` method of each referenced object.
trans-unit.target: 此方法调用每个引用对象的 `Dispose()` 方法。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="Dispose" /> can be called multiple times by other objects.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="Dispose" /> 可以由其他对象多次调用。

trans-unit.source: When overriding <see langword="Dispose(Boolean)" /> be careful not to reference objects that have been previously disposed of in an earlier call to <see langword="Dispose" />.
trans-unit.target: 在重写<see langword="Dispose(Boolean)" />请注意不要引用已释放的以前调用中的对象<see langword="Dispose" />。

trans-unit.source: For more information about how to implement <see langword="Dispose(Boolean)" />, see [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/implementing-dispose.md).
trans-unit.target: 有关如何实现详细信息<see langword="Dispose(Boolean)" />，请参阅[实现 Dispose 方法](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/implementing-dispose.md)。

trans-unit.source: For more information about <see langword="Dispose" /> and <see cref="M:System.Object.Finalize" />, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/unmanaged.md) and [Overriding the Finalize Method](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/8026cb68-fe93-43fc-96c1-c09ad7d64cd3).
trans-unit.target: 有关详细信息<see langword="Dispose" />和<see cref="M:System.Object.Finalize" />，请参阅[清洗向上非托管资源](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/unmanaged.md)和[重写 Finalize 方法](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/8026cb68-fe93-43fc-96c1-c09ad7d64cd3)。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem" /> to test for toolbox support.
Gets a value indicating whether the specified tool is supported by the designer.
<see langword="true" /> if the tool should be enabled on the toolbox; <see langword="false" /> if the document designer doesn't know how to use the tool.
If a tool is supported, it will be enabled in the toolbox when the designer regains focus.
trans-unit.target: 如果支持一种工具，则它将启用工具箱中这是设计器重新获得焦点时。

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, it will be disabled.
trans-unit.target: 否则，它将被禁用。

trans-unit.source: Once a tool is marked as enabled or disabled it cannot be queried again.
trans-unit.target: 后一种工具被标记为启用或禁用它无法再次查询。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.IComponent" /> to associate with the designer.
Initializes the designer with the specified component.
The designer can access the component's site and request services from it in this method.
trans-unit.target: 设计器可以访问组件的站点，并在此方法从它请求服务。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IDictionary" /> that contains the properties for the class of the component.
Adjusts the set of properties the component will expose through a <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor" />.

This <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerFilter> interface method override adds a non-browsable, design-time only `boolean` property named "TrayLargeIcon" to this designer's component at design time.
trans-unit.target: 这<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerFilter>接口方法重写将添加一个非可浏览设计时仅`boolean`名"TrayLargeIcon"为此设计器的组件，在设计时属性。

trans-unit.source: This property is used by the component tray.
trans-unit.target: 组件栏使用此属性。
